BettaCraft World Download – Terms and Conditions
------------------------------------------------

These world downloads are provided for personal use and fan-created content.
By downloading or using these worlds, you agree to the following terms.

------------------------------------------------
Allowed Fan Content
------------------------------------------------
You are welcome to create the following types of content using the world download:

- Let’s Plays
- Exploration videos
- Reaction videos
- World tours
- Commentary videos
- Cinematics
- Fan-made series
- Base-building or “what if I lived here” videos

These uses are fully permitted.

------------------------------------------------
Restrictions (Not Allowed)
------------------------------------------------
To protect BettaCraft SMP and its creators, you may NOT:

- Use the BettaCraft logo or branding.
- Use titles that imply official participation in the SMP.
  Examples:
    • “BettaCraft Season 3 Episode 1”
    • “Joining BettaCraft SMP”
    • “My BettaCraft SMP Series”
    • “BettaCraft S3 Official Episode”
- Claim to be a member of BettaCraft SMP.
- Present your content as official BettaCraft content.
- Monetize content that misrepresents itself as part of BettaCraft.
- Reupload, redistribute, or share this world download (modified or unmodified).
- Claim BettaCraft builds as your own.

You may modify the world for personal use only.  
You may NOT distribute modified or unmodified versions.

Content that violates these rules may be reported for impersonation or misuse.

------------------------------------------------
Allowed Title Examples
------------------------------------------------
These titles are acceptable and clearly indicate fan-made content:

- “Exploring the BettaCraft Season 3 World Download”
- “BettaCraft S3 World Tour (Fan Video)”
- “Fan Playthrough of the BettaCraft World Download”
- “Building a Base in the BettaCraft World Download”

